<br>
1.2.1 What will the minimum system specification be?<br>
<br>
If you have a Intel P-3 or AMD Athlon processor, you'll be able to get away with any 16MB or better D3D capable 3D card. If you have a lesser processor, the tentative minimum spec is:<br>
<br>
P-2 400<br>
128MB Ram<br>
Nvidia GeForce Card<br>
Another 400MB or so of free HDD space.<br>
<br>
The recommended system spec will be a P3 or Athalon Processor with a GeForce 2 or better video card and 256MB of RAM.<br>
<br>
